<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 via-white to-purple-50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl" data-controller="exercise-checker page-viewer" data-page-viewer-image-url-value="<%= asset_path('nvi5_mat/p065/page.png') %>">

  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col-reverse sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4">
        <div class="bg-purple-500 text-white text-md sm:text-xl px-2 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-lg font-bold">NUMERI</div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600">FRAZIONI DECIMALI E NUMERI DECIMALI</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg sm:text-xl cursor-pointer hover:bg-purple-700 transition-colors"
           data-action="click->page-viewer#openOriginal" title="Clicca per vedere la pagina originale">65</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-8 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-blue-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <p class="mb-4">Le frazioni con <strong>denominatore 10, 100, 1000</strong>... si chiamano <strong>frazioni decimali</strong>, ma anche le frazioni che hanno denominatori diversi possono essere trasformate in <strong>frazioni decimali equivalenti</strong>.</p>

    <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p065/p065_01.jpg", class: "w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto rounded shadow-lg mb-4", alt: "Trasformazione frazioni" %>

    <p class="mb-4">Dunque, puoi scrivere 3/5 anche in altri modi:</p>
    <p class="mb-4">con una frazione decimale equivalente, a parole e con un numero decimale.</p>

    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-8 text-lg mb-4">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="font-bold text-2xl mb-2">6</div>
        <div class="border-t-2 border-gray-600 mb-2"></div>
        <div class="font-bold text-2xl">10</div>
      </div>
      <div>sei decimi</div>
      <div class="font-bold text-2xl">0,6</div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-gray-600">I numeri "con la virgola", come sai, si chiamano <strong>numeri decimali</strong>.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-8 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-pink-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">â€¢ Prova tu.</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">Trasforma la frazione 4/25 in una frazione decimale equivalente.</p>
    <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p065/p065_02.jpg", class: "w-full max-w-3xl mx-auto rounded shadow-lg", alt: "Esercizio trasformazione" %>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-100 to-pink-100 rounded-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-700 mb-4">ESERCIZI</h2>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-200 shadow-2xl p-4 mb-4" data-controller="fill-blanks">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">
        <span class="bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">1</span>
        Trasforma le frazioni date in frazioni decimali equivalenti.
      </h3>
      <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p065/p065_03.jpg", class: "w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto rounded shadow-lg", alt: "Esercizio 1" %>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-200 shadow-2xl p-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">
        <span class="bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">2</span>
        Trasforma le frazioni date in frazioni decimali equivalenti, poi esprimile a parole e con un numero decimale. Esegui sul quaderno.
      </h3>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center text-lg">
        <span class="inline-flex flex-col items-center"><span>3</span><span class="border-t border-gray-600 w-full my-0.5"></span><span>4</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex flex-col items-center"><span>3</span><span class="border-t border-gray-600 w-full my-0.5"></span><span>5</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex flex-col items-center"><span>2</span><span class="border-t border-gray-600 w-full my-0.5"></span><span>4</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex flex-col items-center"><span>14</span><span class="border-t border-gray-600 w-full my-0.5"></span><span>25</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex flex-col items-center"><span>13</span><span class="border-t border-gray-600 w-full my-0.5"></span><span>50</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex flex-col items-center"><span>45</span><span class="border-t border-gray-600 w-full my-0.5"></span><span>300</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex flex-col items-center"><span>1</span><span class="border-t border-gray-600 w-full my-0.5"></span><span>25</span></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 text-center"><p class="text-red-600 font-bold text-lg">Quaderno esercizi pp. 209, 213</p></div>
  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls', color: 'purple' %>
</div>
